And she did try to carve herself a jack-o-lana before,
cut and dry... emphasis on the "cut. "

68
00:06:46,397 --> 00:06:50,212
I'm telling you, alicia couldn't have done this.
I know her.

69
00:07:02,617 --> 00:07:03,525
Clark...

70
00:07:05,094 --> 00:07:07,171
lana doesn't want to see you.

71
00:07:14,255 --> 00:07:17,886
I'm getting a funny sense
of déjà vu here, mr. Kent.

72
00:07:17,947 --> 00:07:20,317
Haven't we acted out
this particular charade before?

73
00:07:20,363 --> 00:07:23,224
This is different, sheriff.
Alicia did not attack lana.

74
00:07:23,270 --> 00:07:24,624
She was with me.

75
00:07:25,363 --> 00:07:29,178
I better not find out you're covering
for that girlfriend of yours, mr. Kent.

76
00:07:29,240 --> 00:07:34,963
Having you as an alibi is the only thing
keeping me from tossing her tail in jail.

77
